-- Enea Appoints Former Vattenfall Manager Bil to Commercial Post
-- B y   K a t y a   A n d r u s z
-- 2012-02-25T11:04:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-25/enea-appoints-former-vattenfall-manager-bil-to-commercial-post.html
Enea SA (ENA) ,  Poland ’s third-largest
power group, appointed Janusz Bil, a former  Vattenfall AB (VATT) 
manager in the country, to oversee commercial matters.  Bil, who has also worked for German power company  RWE AG (RWE) ’s
Polish division and for Poland’s energy regulator, will take his
board post on March 19, the Poznan-based company said in a
regulatory statement late yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katya Andrusz in Warsaw at 
 kandrusz@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  